{"tid":2147311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【制裁 11 官】港府轟美「起底」官員違私隱　惟商經局亦曾公開被制裁者詳細資料","createTime":"2020-08-09T07:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T07:21:16.000Z","uid":339805,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1cb9a1882051f1a05fe4caceb366c978b4a405","tid":2147311,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"美國日前宣布制裁 11 名中港官員，包括行政長官林鄭月娥、律政司司長鄭若驊、警務處長鄧炳強、中聯辦主任駱惠寧等，並公開相關官員的個人資料。政府及多位官員昨日相繼發聲明譴責，斥美國政府故意公開官員個人資料做法「可悲」，有如獲國家認可的「起底」；同被制裁的政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞亦批評有關行為是肆意「起底」、流氓行徑。不過翻查資料，發現商經局亦曾公開大量被制裁者的個人資料，包括姓名、出生日期、證件號碼等。人民力量陳志全認為，公開被制裁者資料是國際慣常做法，「唔該班香港高官鬧美國前做吓功課先！」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/制裁-11-官-港府轟美-起底-官員違私隱-惟商經局亦曾公開被制裁者詳細資料/?fbclid=IwAR3ElUj-61m4AWTKU8jMuc2S34SC1S0xsr-Cujo96o6PEVsHofajSkQ4UEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-11-%E5%AE%98-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E8%BD%9F%E7%BE%8E-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E9%81%95%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1-%E6%83%9F%E5%95%86%E7%B6%93%E5%B1%80%E4%BA%A6%E6%9B%BE%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E8%80%85%E8%A9%B3%E7%B4%B0%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ElUj-61m4AWTKU8jMuc2S34SC1S0xsr-Cujo96o6PEVsHofajSkQ4UEU&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=49c68af6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-11-%E5%AE%98-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E8%BD%9F%E7%BE%8E-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E9%81%95%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1-%E6%83%9F%E5%95%86%E7%B6%93%E5%B1%80%E4%BA%A6%E6%9B%BE%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E8%80%85%E8%A9%B3%E7%B4%B0%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ElUj-61m4AWTKU8jMuc2S34SC1S0xsr-Cujo96o6PEVsHofajSkQ4UEU&h=e4979b1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/制裁-11-官-港府轟美-起底-官員違私隱-惟商經局亦曾公開被制裁者詳細資料/?fbclid=IwAR3ElUj-61m4AWTKU8jMuc2S34SC1S0xsr-Cujo96o6PEVsHofajSkQ4UEU</a>"},{"pid":"60c0a7ac7ebf672c53ab1a58f10998fe35